      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm writing this. everything just feels so heavy. my funding got cut today and the lab results for the last six months are basically garbage. i've put everything into this—literally everything—and it's just falling apart. i'm so tired of fighting to keep my head above water. it feels like there's no way to actually stop the noise or the pressure. i just want to be able to rest, like, actually rest for once.",
